<p><i>Chief Financial Officer (CFO)</i></p>
<p>Steve Collins joined AXIS in July 2011 as the Chief Financial Officer (CFO). Steve has a wealth of international mobile telecommunications experience and has been a qualified accountant for over 15 years. Before joining AXIS Steve spent the last three years as the CFO of Vodafone Egypt, prior to this Steve held CFO positions in both Vodafone Portugal and Sweden together with gaining extensive experience in the UK mobile market. Steve graduated from Econ University College of Wales and is member of The Chartered Institute of Management Accountants.</p></td>
