<p><i>Director of Sales</i></p>
<p>Syakieb Ahmad Sungkar has over 20 years of working experience in one of the Indonesian leading telecommunication company, PT Indosat, where for the last 11 years he was responsible in the development and operations of the sales, distributions and marketing of the company.</p> <p>In 2000 he was appointed as the GM Sales and Marketing at PT IM3. Syakieb was appointed as the Vice President Direct Sales, Consumer Market PT Indosat in 2003, whereby he was responsible for the channel development and distributions. Following this appointment, he then has been involved in various sales and distribution projects and operations in PT Indosat. His last position in PT Indosat is the Regional Sales Director. Syakieb Ahmad Sungkar graduated from Institute of Technology Bandung (ITB) in 1986.</p></td>
