<td valign="top"><h4 style="margin:0;">MICHAEL McPHAIL</h4>
<p><i>Director/Chief Technology Officer (CTO)</i></p>
<p>Michael McPhail (Mike) was appointed as CTO of AXIS in April 2011. Mike has worked in AXIS from January 2008 and in his previous role as Head of Implementation, he was responsible for the deployment of AXIS network throughout Indonesia. Prior to coming to AXIS, Mike worked in DiGi Telecommunications Malaysia, where he managed multiple key and high profile cross-functional projects, which assisted DiGi to grow from a distant number 3 operator to number 2 prepaid operator. Before coming to Asia, Mike worked for Cesky Mobil in the Czech Republic in a number of roles within the planning and operations teams. Mike, who has spent more than 11 years in telecommunications, has a Master's Degree with Merit in Civil Engineering from Heriot-Watt University, Edinburgh.</p></td>
