<p><i>Chief Marketing Officer (CMO)</i></p>
<p>Daniel Horan joined AXIS in October 2011 as the Chief Marketing Officer (CMO). Daniel has worked for more than 10 years in the mobile industry with Vodafone in senior marketing and sales roles across five countries, most recently as the Chief Commercial Officer of Vodafone Qatar, prior to that in Hungary, The United Kingdom, Netherlands, and Australia. Daniel also worked for several years in marketing roles with companies like Sony Corporation.</p>
<p>Daniel has completed studies in universities including Henley on Thames, United Kingdom, IMD in Switerland. He also joined several courses and training programs accross countries, like Australia, Netherlands, Switzerland, and Germany.</p>
<p>Daniel is a keen sports fan who loves viewing and participating in sports including; Swimming, Cycling and Golf, he has completed 2 Ironman Triathalons. A favourite quote from Daniel is from a Japanese proverb, "Fall down seven times, get up eight".</p></td>
